Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:03.89,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.27,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.26,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:15.43,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:15.43,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:17.38,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nabikanai nagasarenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:17.38,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give in. I won't be dragged away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima kanjiru koto ni sunao de itai no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay honest to the way I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:21.32,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:21.32,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:23.43,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nando demo umarekawaru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:23.43,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be reborn as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:25.38,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kanashimi mo dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:25.38,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my sadness with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:28.01,J,,0000,0000,0000,,hashiridasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:28.01,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.45,J,,0000,0000,0000,,tanoshii uragiri ni atte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.45,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, betrayal can be pleasurable...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:39.75,J,,0000,0000,0000,,torawarenai atashi ga koko ni iru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:39.75,E,,0000,0000,0000,,But I stand right here - not giving in to temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:42.14,J,,0000,0000,0000,,tarinai tsukinai nandatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:42.14,E,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enough," "not enough," whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.24,J,,0000,0000,0000,,motto hizumasete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.24,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:48.10,J,,0000,0000,0000,,pataan kashita konna sekai ja
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:48.10,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Living in this routine-laden world...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:51.12,J,,0000,0000,0000,,jibun ga dare nano ka wakaranakunaru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:51.12,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...is enough to make you forget who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.31,J,,0000,0000,0000,,waku ni hamaritakunai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.31,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be stereotyped...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:58.44,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kimetsukenaide yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:58.44,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...so don't make assumptions about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:02.20,J,,0000,0000,0000,,michi naki michi wo yuku no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:02.20,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to blaze my own trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:05.60,J,,0000,0000,0000,,soko ni itatte matteitatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:05.60,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will ever be accomplished...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:08.49,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nani mo hajimaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:08.49,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you just stand around waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:09.23,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:09.23,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.40,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nabikanai nagasarenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.40,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give in. I won't be dragged away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:15.00,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima kanjiru koto ni sunao de itai no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:15.00,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay honest to the way I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:19.90,J,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no omoidoori ni wa sasenai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:19.90,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:20.91,J,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:20.91,E,,0000,0000,0000,,chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:23.17,J,,0000,0000,0000,,nando demo umarekawaru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:23.17,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be reborn as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:25.14,J,,0000,0000,0000,,kanashimi wo dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:25.14,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my sadness with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:28.68,J,,0000,0000,0000,,hashiridasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:28.68,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.32,J,,0000,0000,0000,,anata no moto ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.32,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm past the point of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.37,J,,0000,0000,0000,,mou kaerenai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.37,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot go back to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:36.30,J,,0000,0000,0000,,atashi wa atashirashiku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:36.30,E,,0000,0000,0000,,On my own terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:37.87,J,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna chAngE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:37.87,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wanna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:52.28,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:53.63,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.59,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.58,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:13.11,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:21.07,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter who dies, I'll still\Nget good research specimens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:25.70,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,That was an impressive Cero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:30.09,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bastard still\Nhas power left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.49,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:37.97,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to finish\Nhim off, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:43.14,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him. I pity your\Nfoolish judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:48.47,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,To me, that's all it took.\NA good finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.65,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,But I suppose it was too\Nmuch to ask from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.19,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:08.66,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,You can feel for yourself whether\Nit's too much to ask or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.69,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.74,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I've always
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:16.63,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.07,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,-You're in the way!\N-You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.40,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,-Get lost!\N-Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.46,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:02.76,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.45,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,He really is a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.80,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.51,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really annoy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:34.72,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.38,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Has he gone crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:40.56,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Un-Unforgivable! Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.38,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Un-Un...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.59,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Un-Un-Un...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.56,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Un-Un...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:48.05,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.83,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.90,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.15,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.34,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,You're really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:30.54,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,The name of my Resurrección is Ira.\NI'm a beast of rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:34.22,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Anger becomes my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:39.98,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, make me angrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:43.14,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Your deaths will be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:46.55,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,that much more pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.30,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.78,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of it, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:55.73,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Just kill each other already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.79,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets any larger,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:02.21,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a difficult time\Ndissecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.65,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Tosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.80,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Tosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come down here, Tosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.55,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:21.62,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you become\Na Soul Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.16,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it for your friend\Nwho passed away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:26.55,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it to carry out\Nyour form of justice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.98,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, Komamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:33.55,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can see with my\Neyes is the least bloody path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:36.51,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Justice is always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:40.32,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,The path I follow is justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.36,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Friend of Tosen, whose\Nname I do not know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:58.99,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What would you have\Nsaid to stop Tosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.87,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Komamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.51,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Captain Tosen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.14,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,will ever come back\Nhere again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.35,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:23.87,B2,KOMAMURA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's find a way to\Nopen Tosen's eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:32.78,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.45,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,One down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.92,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.94,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:12.45,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.19,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:19.91,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,I...I couldn't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.05,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,What a fierce look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.51,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes look as if
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.01,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,they've come back to life for the\Nfirst time in a hundred years,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.29,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji Hirako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:57.49,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.53,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, then come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:09.39,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I shall make an exception for you\Nand fight you with my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:13.62,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:14.96,B2,HACHIGEN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:17.55,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to ask you for this\Nin your current condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.53,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,but take care of Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.43,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you can\Nto keep her alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.25,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Just until Ichigo returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:28.72,B2,HACHIGEN,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.06,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.45,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,"Until Ichigo returns," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:49.54,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You trust that boy quite\Na lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.41,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's something you\Ncan't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:56.05,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Not someone who can't even\Ntrust his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:11:01.24,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Believing is the same as relying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.29,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,That is something the weak do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.06,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,We have no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:11.61,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty rich coming from a\Nguy with that many henchmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:15.64,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,You used your silver tongue to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:18.07,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,trick your subordinates\Ninto trusting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.01,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:27.49,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I've never told my subordinates\Nto trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:31.95,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I told them to follow me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:35.25,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,but I never told them\Nto trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:42.47,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I always told them never to\Ntrust anyone, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:51.78,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,But sadly, there aren't any who\Nare strong enough to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:58.51,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,All creatures are unable to survive\Nunless they trust and obey
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:02.26,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,someone who is better\Nthan they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.53,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,To escape that pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:12.05,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,those who are better than others\Nsearch for their superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.81,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are superior,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:19.30,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,search for even stronger individuals\Nthey can believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:24.02,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Thus the king of everything\Nwas born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.39,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Thus the god of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:30.76,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:37.31,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't believe me yet,\NShinji Hirako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:44.46,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take my time and show\Nyou which god you should believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:49.70,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You can decide on what\Nto believe afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.81,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:09.00,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected Lord Aizen\Nto go to the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:13.39,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Since Lord Aizen has\Nmade a move,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:18.86,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I should take you on\Nwith my true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.77,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,True...power?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:25.24,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Your Bankai, huh? Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.08,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I shall use mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.22,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,My Bankai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.78,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:37.75,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Aizen gave me a power that\Nis far better than a Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.55,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Tosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:53.52,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.65,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.86,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Tosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.71,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how far you've fallen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:18.41,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Tosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.72,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:44.80,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Hollowfication...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:50.32,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...Is that a Hollowfication,\NCaptain Tosen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:53.03,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.95,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:07.88,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.39,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Tenken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.16,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:48.46,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,What...is...this power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.32,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,How odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:21.84,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,That half-Soul Reaper boy\Nyou consider as an ally
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:25.11,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,has the power of Hollowfication\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:31.84,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Must you scorn me so much\Nfor gaining this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:38.27,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,He...Ichigo Kurosaki did\Nnot Hollowfy by choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.81,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,But you are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:45.90,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,As a Soul Reaper, you had\Nmore than enough strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:49.32,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you went astray\Nof your own volition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:53.28,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is that of corruption, Tosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.15,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Corruption?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:17:00.60,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,How is it corrupt for Soul Reapers\Nto become closer to Hollows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.45,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Such words come from a\Nnarrow-minded dualism
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.92,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,that deems Soul Reapers and\NHollows as good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.32,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:11.86,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed your comrades,\Nyou betrayed your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.67,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,and you even betrayed\Nyour subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:17.49,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,All for the sake of gaining\Nexcessive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.35,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,That is corruption!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.96,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Komamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:34.57,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I didn't step\Nin far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.53,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,How naïve of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.92,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:41.49,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I instinctively dodged\Nit by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:45.08,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I draw my sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.36,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I position myself to always be able\Nto dodge everything by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:53.58,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me that,\NCaptain Tosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:58.23,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Tosen, it's because\Nof you that I was able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.69,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Hisagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:11.39,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you called me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:16.00,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to\Ntalk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.65,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Tosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:23.62,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Please relieve me from the\Nposition of Seat Officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.83,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what\Nthis was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:31.30,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about your mistake\Nduring training yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.64,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone starts off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.03,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,This is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.13,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't fall behind because\NI made a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.84,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,or because I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.47,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:48.39,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, when I went to train\Nin the World of the Living,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.77,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I injured my right eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.98,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I've been no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.73,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I draw my sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.52,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,whenever I face an enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:01.93,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I always feel discouraged!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:09.58,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Tosen...I...I'm\Nafraid of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:16.03,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,"Afraid of battle," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:22.98,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you should\Nremain an officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:29.23,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing for a\Nwarrior to have is not power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.31,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,It is a heart that fears battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:34.94,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,A heart that fears...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.33,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.01,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm afraid of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.24,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,You, Captain Tosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:45.59,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot see. How can I\Nnot be afraid of battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.24,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Holding my sword
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:55.34,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,and even taking a step forward\Nlike this are incredibly terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:59.34,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Fearing battle, allows you\Nto pick up your sword
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:04.80,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,and fight for those who\Nare also afraid of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:11.70,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are not afraid\Nto hold their swords
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:14.65,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,do not have the right\Nto hold swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.12,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:21.61,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly fear battle from\Nthe bottom of your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:28.24,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,then you have gained something\Nthat is invaluable to a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:39.34,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I...I cannot understand,\NCaptain Tosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.10,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Those were your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:45.13,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you discard\Neverything for power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:50.77,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, what are\Nyou afraid of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:59.15,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Cap...tain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.30,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Tosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.57,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:16.71,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,These past hundred\Nyears, my fear was
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.89,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,being assimilated into\Nyou Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:20.49,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,and to die as one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.98,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:28.97,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Kokujo Tengen Myo-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:38.98,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Tosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.69,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I will do whatever it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.90,B2,KOMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,to open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:56.84,J,,0000,0000,0000,,koe sae ushinattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:56.84,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I was stripped of my voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:03.64,J,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa koko de utau darou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:03.64,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be here, singing my song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:11.18,J,,0000,0000,0000,,koko kara hibike
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:11.18,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Echo out from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:19.98,J,,0000,0000,0000,,miminari ni kesareta seijaku no yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:19.98,E,,0000,0000,0000,,The ringing in my ears stole the night's tranquility.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:26.92,J,,0000,0000,0000,,katachi nai mirai wo oikaketeta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:26.92,E,,0000,0000,0000,,I chased a future that doesn't exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:34.08,J,,0000,0000,0000,,sono te wa kuu wo tsukandekita kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:34.08,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet all I caught was nothing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:37.72,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to it! Listen to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:41.67,J,,0000,0000,0000,,deai ga tsumuideku merodi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:41.67,E,,0000,0000,0000,,The melody of the people we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:45.08,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! Listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:47.97,J,,0000,0000,0000,,oto ni kawaru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:47.97,E,,0000,0000,0000,,...as I become sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:57.16,J,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa mada konna ni chiisa na kono koe ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:57.16,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Though my voice is still small and meager today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.69,J,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka wa tsuyoku hibiiteiku kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:03.69,E,,0000,0000,0000,,One day it shall gloriously resound.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.32,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to it! Listen to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:11.16,J,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashiku yuriokosu merodi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:11.16,E,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet melody that'll awake\Nyou from your slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.60,E,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:19.91,J,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2800)}kimi ga omou kimi e
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:19.91,E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2800)}My song will reach the person you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.34,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'm going to\Nbelieve you, Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:26.00,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I would have provided you with\Na huge feast and a castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:28.40,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,as well as anything\Nyou could desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:30.47,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,If only you would have\Nbelieved in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:31.09,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:32.61,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:34.72,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Give me a second\Nto think it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:35.71,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Say goodbye to your old self!\NThe Charismatic Dr. Mayuri Kurotsuchi's\NMagical Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:37.75,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Dr. Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.03,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to help resolve\Nany issues
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:40.52,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,you may have with\Nyour appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:42.29,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a8}Before surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:42.29,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2\i1}Gloomy single-edged eyelid...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:42.29,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Case 1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:42.66,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Going from a gloomy\Nsingle-edged eyelid
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:45.17,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a8}After surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:45.17,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2\i1}Turns into bright double-edged eyelid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:45.17,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Case 1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.08,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,to a bright double-edged\Neyelid is a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.21,0:23:47.80,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Case 2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.21,0:23:47.80,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a8}Before surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:47.96,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Think there's no hope for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:49.42,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a8}After surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:49.42,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Case 2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:49.51,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, think again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:51.55,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a8}Before surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:51.55,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2\i1}Reconstruct your body\Nat the cellular level.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:51.55,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Case 3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:54.07,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,We can also reconstruct your\Nbody at the cellular level.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:54.05,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a8}After surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:54.05,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2\i1}To become a completely\Ndifferent you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:54.05,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Case 3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:56.05,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I didn't go through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:57.21,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This is excessive advertising!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:23:58.44,B2,HIYORI,0000,0000,0000,,You want a beating, baldy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.26,0:24:02.11,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the following to\Nrequest our brochures.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.97,B2,MAYURI,0000,0000,0000,,There are currently trials\Navailable as well.